query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind in ('cast','complete') AND mi.info not in ('Faroese','Vietnamese','Zulu','Mongolian','Italian','Chinese','English','Kyrgyz','Slovenian') AND it2.info in ('birth date','other works','LD pressing plant','LD label','release dates','LD picture format','genres','runtimes','birth name') AND it1.info in ('LD certification','essays','LD quality program','height','agent address','LD catalog number','interviews','LD analog left','LD language','LD year','LD dialogue intellegibility','salary history','other literature','birth date','runtimes') AND t.production_year > 1995 AND t.title not like '%microphone%' AND t.title not like '%journey%' AND t.title not like '%suitcase%' AND k.keyword not like '%vengeful%' AND k.keyword not like '%desire%' AND k.keyword not like '%martial%' AND cct1.kind in ('crew','cast') AND (n.name like '%K%' OR n.name like '%c%' OR n.name like '%G%' OR n.name like '%v%') AND mi_idx.info > '2.0'
